<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>Joy trains her brain</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/164962752/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Joy trains her brain" src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/70/164962752_336784c8da_m.jpg" height="180" width="240" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>I bought the <a href="http://www.nintendo.com/channel/ds">DS Lite</a> that I've been craving for so long this morning.  Joy's been quite taken with <a href="http://www.brainage.com/">Brain Age</a>.</p>

<p>I'm hoping to get it back off her soon so that I can indulge in a little more <a href="http://mario.nintendo.com/">Super Mario</a>.</p>
        </p>

